org.apache.flink.runtime.clusterframework.types

类 ResourceProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.clusterframework.types.ResourceProfile
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ResourceProfile>

    public class ResourceProfile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ResourceProfile>
    Describe the resource profile of the slot, either when requiring or offering it. The profile can be checked whether it can match another profile's requirement, and furthermore we may calculate a matching score to decide which profile we should choose when we have lots of candidate slots.

    Resource Profiles have a total ordering, defined by comparing these fields in sequence:

    1. Memory Size
    2. CPU cores
